.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, september, october, february
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, family, drama, disaster
1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the person watching family movies##8
3. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
5. the person who's birthday is in july is the person watching western movies##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | october   | september         | february   | july    |
| Movie-Genre         | family | disaster | drama | western |

