.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, baking, skydiving, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, jazz, r&b, rock
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is baking##7
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the fan of r&b##5
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is camping##7
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the fan of rock##8
5. the fan of rock is somewhere between the person who's hobby is baking and the fan of jazz##7
6. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
7. the fan of jazz is not to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##8
8. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | baking   | skydiving | sudoku | camping    |
| Music-Genre         | techno | rock   | r&b   | jazz |

