.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, mexican, dutch, thai
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, musician, social-worker, police-officer
1. the police-officer is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the musician is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
3. the dutch is on the right of the social-worker##1
4. the chef is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
5. the polish is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
6. the thai is not to the left of the musician##8
7. the thai is the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality          | thai | polish | mexican  | dutch |
| Job   | musician   | police-officer         | social-worker | chef |

