.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, january, june
4 different pets are kept: cat, mouse, dog, frog
1. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
2. the owner of the frog is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the owner of the dog##7
3. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
4. the owner of the frog is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8
5. the owner of the frog is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | july      | january | april | june   |
| Pet      | cat | dog | frog  | mouse |

