2. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the person who's hobby is collecting##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Hobby     | woodworking | collecting | board-games | photography     |
| Pet   | goldfish   | mouse        | fish          | snake |

