.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, animation, action, spy
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, monopoly, backgammon
1. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person playing mah-jongg##2
2. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
4. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
5. the person playing canasta is the person playing canasta##1
6. the person watching action movies is not the person playing monopoly##6
7. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
8. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person playing canasta##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy   | romance | action | animation |
| Game     | backgammon | canasta       | mah-jongg  | monopoly    |

