.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
House: craftsman, modern, cottage, futuristic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, blues, house, techno
1. the cottage house is not to the right of the fan of techno##8
2. the fan of folk is not to the right of the modern house##8
3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
4. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
5. the cottage house is between the fan of techno and the fan of house##2
6. the modern house is on the far left##1
7. the cottage house is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| House    | modern        | futuristic | cottage      | craftsman    |
| Music-Genre   | folk | house   | blues | techno |

