3. the dutch is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3
6. the malaysian is somewhere between the polish and the person playing bridge##7
7. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Game   | mah-jongg | bridge         | monopoly    | poker       |
| Nationality      | dutch | japanese | malaysian | polish |

