3. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
4. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing monopoly and the craftsman house##2
5. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
6. the tower house is between the futuristic house and the victorian house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
