.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, writing, fishing
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, orange, white, ebony
 1. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who likes white##1
 4. the person who likes white is not to the right of the person who likes orange##8
 5. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 6. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 7. the person who likes orange is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the person who likes white##8
 9. the person who likes orange is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby          | magic-tricks    | writing | dancing | fishing |
| Color   | fuchsia | ebony  | white     | orange    |

