.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-17::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, dunhill, havana, bolivar
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, mouse, turtle, snake
1. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the dunhill-smoker##8
2. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the dunhill-smoker##8
3. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
4. the havana-smoker is not the owner of the snake##6
5. the bolivar-smoker is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
7. the havana-smoker is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
8. the havana-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |    4    |
| Cigar           | havana | bolivar | dunhill | davidoff   |
| Pet   | turtle       | snake      | mouse    | guinea-pig |

