.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, september, march, february
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, sports, disaster, romance
1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8
3. the person watching sports movies is the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching romance movies is the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person watching sports movies and the person who's birthday is in february##2
7. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday    | february        | september | april | march |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | disaster | sports   | adventure    |

