.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, davidoff, blend, bongani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, water-polo, badminton, lacrosse
1. the bongani-smoker is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
2. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the blend-smoker##8
3. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere between the blend-smoker and the bongani-smoker##7
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the pall-mall-smoker##5
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
6. the person who's sport is handball is not to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
7. the davidoff-smoker is not to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar         | pall-mall  | bongani | davidoff  | blend  |
| Sport   | handball | water-polo   | lacrosse | badminton |

