.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, mauve, grey, black
House: modern, futuristic, gothic-revival, wooden
1. the futuristic house is not the person who likes ivory##6
2. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the wooden house##1
3. the person who likes black is not to the left of the wooden house##8
4. the person who likes grey is the modern house##1
5. the person who likes black is somewhere between the futuristic house and the modern house##7
6. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
7. the gothic-revival house is between the wooden house and the person who likes grey##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Color         | mauve    | black | ivory | grey |
| House   | futuristic | wooden      | gothic-revival     | modern     |

 